	<h1>ABOUT US</h1>
	<p> WORLD Bank is a high quality,customer centric and service driven Bank.Since inception in 2004,WORLD BANK has grown into a "Full Service Commercial Bank" providing a complete range of products,services and technology driven digital offerings,catering to cooperate,MSME & retail customers.WORLD BANK operates its Investment banking, Merchant banking & Brokerage businesses through WORLD SECURITIES and its Mutual Fund business through WORLD Asset Management (India) Limited, both wholly owned subsidiaries of the Bank. Headquartered in Mumbai, it has a pan-India presence across all 28 states and 9 Union Territories in India including an IBU at GIFT City, and a Representative Office in Dubai.The Bank's consolidated total assets stood at Rs. 14.76 trillion at September 2020.WORLD Bank currently has a network of 5288 branches and 15158 ATMs across India. </p>
